势必以损人的目的出发，以害己的结果告终。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-e02ad2ae5e775438770b717122a86f04_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "748 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/455060718"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyN6Y/vT27PUQEAMaCDYzNDA0NDQyIPCQ6YMGMBE4qwVAB3IJNDU1MDYwNzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1618661408.2634196", "card_id": "Q_454086545", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 181}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "一直瞄准风口的小米都要造车了，机械专业是不是有救了？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-41776a5222289e763c5d99c3931cb33e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "650 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454086545"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyN6Y/vT27PUQEAMaCDYzMTg3NzU1IKKqy4MGMCA4kAZACHIJNDU0MDg2NTQ1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1618661408.2638338", "card_id": "Q_454792574", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 204}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "空城计的时候司马懿为什么不先派一个士兵前去探一下敌情？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed285a2f5cdd28a830dae1a554399858_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "550 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454792574"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyN6Y/vT27PUQEAMaCDYzMzQ0ODE4IMuL4IMGMAw48QJACXIJNDU0NzkyNTc0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1618661408.2641888", "card_id": "Q_451449283", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 219}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "新版的国标红绿灯设计合理吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这两组的通行规则是一样的，上面一组很容易让人产生困惑，请问这样设计的理由是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "htt